| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-0869 — Recovery Inhibition (blackbasta)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 725d2b51-13bc-5499-946e-5e5fc45a59a8"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
